{"type": "article", "id": 60825, "title": "一款没有实际功能的装饰眼镜，灵感来自ins滤镜｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2019-01-30T23:06:24Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 53517, "name": "Fredericia"}, {"id": 56370, "name": "Geckeler Michels"}, {"id": 56371, "name": "Work & Co"}, {"id": 51098, "name": "JUNIPER"}, {"id": 56372, "name": "A BATHING APE®"}, {"id": 56373, "name": "Bentel Brothers"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 11, "praise_count": 69, "image": "img/article/article_show/201901310101140KplzOT1vV8ZNW4E.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} span.s4 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none; color: #2965a8; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #2965a8} span.s5 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>The Squiggle Glasses by Nikolas Bentel and his brother Lukas</h3><p>一个名为 Bentel Brothers 的品牌，总是推出各种稀奇古怪的产品，最近它们更是推出了一个没有实际功能性的 Squiggle 眼镜系列，灵感源自 Instagram 的滤镜。</p><p>这款眼镜看起来就像是纽约 MoMA 博物馆设计商店里的纪念品。它是一款半透明的波浪形眼镜，共有两款配色与不同的眼镜臂供你选择，它不是一副具有功能性的眼镜，也没有任何防晒度数或视力矫正功能，完全就是一款玩具眼镜。</p><p>设计者说：“我们想要制作永久的东西，希望透过这副眼镜，来把社交媒体上的滤镜实物化。”而波浪形状及其花哨颜色，同时也可以把它当作成一件艺术品或儿童玩具作收藏。售价 55 美元起，<a href=\"https://www.bentelbrothers.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190131010221VXYaq2muT6clfKQv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.851100\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190131010201uWCdcPBRv5SNOUm9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.598562\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190131010202xPhkIcAVUGvZ9bwi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.490694\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190131010203wcPMevZuX8UfQCK1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.768190\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2019013101020448KOLy3HmlkEDMnN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562606\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190131010203AuqeCs5TjI8KX6J7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.273689\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>TYPE 1 BAPEX WATCHES</h3><p>日本街头潮牌 A BATHING APE® 素来喜欢从一些既有的东西上寻找灵感，再为其添入新元素为产品带来焕新面貌。比如以 Rolex 表款为灵感所诞生的 BAPEX 就是一款经典之作，更是每季必出的单品。</p><p>最近，A BATHING APE® 以 TYPE 1 BAPEX 腕表为基础，将品牌近期主推的 ABC Camo 元素添入腕表中，还首次带来尼龙表带版本，令腕表顿时变得年轻感，更容易搭配日常造型。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190131010243bQyziNjeTx0sSBP2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190131010243MOid52RTSe1PHnkE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201901310102449ZtR1bwrcK3nSCkv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>The Axis Collection by Miren Lasnier for JUNIPER</h3><p>纽约布鲁克林的照明品牌 JUNIPER 一直扮演着当代照明领域的开拓者的角色，最近它们引入了 Axis X Vertical Suspension，重新诠释 2018 年推出的 Axis 系列产品，以及四款受 JUNIPER 标志性 THIN 枝形吊灯启发的新灯具设计。</p><p>Miren Lasnier 为 JUNIPER 设计的 Axis 系列，通过模块化设计展现出形式和光线的平衡。其他的轨道模块化系统灯饰，也是经过精心设计，适用于室外。框架具有防水功能，同时保持谨慎和极简的风格。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190131010310kNCMrtPbe0jYFgup.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190131010310rvRVl3FZJoec9B6d.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190131010311JW4mdoXgky2tTx8r.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190131010311Or1LtnkREvgJFPSj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190131010311U5ey8rVpNOknW3cH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190131010312pKLuHRDNYmIZe93o.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201901310103134KNZl0r2ngy7E53U.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.juniper-design.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">JUNIPER</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>The Nova mobile office pod by Work &amp; Co&nbsp;</h3><p>Nova Pod 是一款移动办公室解决方案，意在为如今随时移动的灵活工作群体提供便利，内置快速无线网络、智能电视、Apple TV、打印机、咖啡机、迷你冰箱、充电站、电源插座、浴室和自来水等等。Nova Pod 是由开普敦联合办公空间 Work &amp; Co 开发的，可以选择一些视野较好的城市区域办公，被看作是“非办公室”办公空间的创新之作。</p><p>Work＆Co 联合创始人 Jolize Pienaar 表示：“寻找灵感，同时注重成效，是创造 Nova 的强烈动机之一。我们鼓励用户沉浸在不同的风景中，同时坐拥装备齐全的空间，解放思想和生产力。”</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190131010351gCpUNi9jWh5nZ7yA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190131010351mgiMUHYC9BVrPjGc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190131010351K4iqJMVd5uchPjEw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2019013101035208TusdGFytNhXORE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.030880\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190131010352WLPFmtZXhe9jNd6f.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190131010352cSsTxzUYijQFB3Zu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562606\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190131010354kZH0AgTr6xSBn3Ku.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201901310103542sRcMgKL5m9quTSb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667936\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.dezeen.com/2019/01/25/nova-pod-solar-powered-coworking-office-design/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dezeen</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Acme Chair by Geckeler Michels for Fredericia</h3><p>柏林设计工作室 Geckeler Michels 推出了一款名为 Acme 的座椅，是为丹麦家具品牌 Fredericia 量身而做。</p><p>Acme 座椅算是对经典贝壳椅的重新想象，设计上更为大胆，圆形和方形两种对比鲜明的几何形状，以令人惊讶的方式整合在一起，为用户提供舒适的就坐体验。独特的腿部设计又赋予了每一款椅子不一样的性格。</p><p>这款耐用且坐感舒适的聚丙烯材质椅子，适用于公共和私人空间。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190131010510f1Dj6m3QlZGSWkPi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333125\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190131010510Sq0m7KPZxbOtnDyJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.332500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2019013101051098ideFmvhz5RHqQy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201901310105113ixSI5T12zZsOD0y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.332500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190131010511PmY5Nu0negyFBEfG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.332500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190131010511DI5aO8domsHrY7xV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.332500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201901310105114Bet7Do5MNwZ9CJg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.332500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190131010511sdbwOitIyKXWVpx3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.332500\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.geckelermichels.com/projects/acme/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Geckeler Michels</a></figcaption></figure></div><p class=\"\"><br></p>"}